&lt;p&gt;Content creation, editing, and management:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Long and short-form content creation for various channels including the blog, social media, ads, website, decks, one-pagers, reports, questionnaires, applications, and other various types of content (training will be provided as needed by the Head of Content).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Will be specifically responsible for PR content as we expand our publicity and outreach.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;May assist the Head of Content in proofreading and editing third-party created content.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Occasionally may help with preparing content briefs for freelance writers as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist the HoC with the preparation of a comprehensive content calendar, especially for PR.&lt;/li&gt;
