&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Paystand&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Paystand is a hungry, fast-growing, Series-C startup with three locations! Nestled in the beautiful Santa Cruz mountains, just south of Silicon Valley is where we started. We have our offices in amazing and historic Guadalajara Mexico and Salt Lake City with the dramatic backdrops of the mountains of Utah.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our mission is to unlock capital efficiency for enterprise businesses through our transformative&amp;nbsp;“Payments as a Service” platform. Our smart billing and payment network uses revolutionary internet, blockchain, and FinTech services to digitize receivables, automate processing, reduce time-to-cash, lower transaction costs, and produce new revenue for our clients. Paystand is venture-backed, having been consistently recognized as one of the top innovators in FinTech, and fastest growing companies in the world.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Paystand is looking for a Marketing Ops Specialist to join us in creating the future of commercial payments infrastructure. This is an opportunity to work for one of the hottest, early-stage companies in financial technology. You will be a part of a growing team that is fundamentally re-architecting global payments in the digital era with core blockchain technology. We are a team of disruptors and technologists paving the way for a new financial system, with a passion to bring more openness, transparency, and health to the global economy.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role At A Glance&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;The role of our Marketing Operations Specialist is to manage the funnel and attribution process that is used across the organization. In this role, you will drive insights into campaign performance by building and managing workflows across our Hubspot Marketing automation platforms and CRM. You will have the opportunity to work with business and technical teams across the three offices to make an impact on marketing analytics and influence the operations roadmap.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;This is a high-impact opportunity to drive improvements in internal process and funnel velocity that lead directly to pipeline and growth.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
