&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Assisting in the direction and development of compliance with laws, regulatory requirements, policies, and procedures systematically across our exchange&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Facilitating information requests from state and federal governments, partners, and other regulatory bodies&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
