&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Desire and drive to help build a Compliance program capable of supporting the growth and scale of a revolutionary company in the crypto space&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Proven experience troubleshooting and discovering solutions quickly and effectively with exemplary written and verbal communication skills&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
