&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Help mentor other designers on the team, providing feedback and guidance based on your experiences.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
